<p><strong>No. of airports:</strong> 3 – Calgary, Montreal &amp; Vancouver.</p>
<p><strong>Fly from:</strong> Direct from London Gatwick and London Heathrow. Most regional airports via Amsterdam, or add ons with British Airways from Birmingham, Glasgow, Edinburgh &amp; Manchester on to Heathrow and then direct to Calgary.</p>]]></facts>
